text: haey karophlasabdaur rveang peloyb ning pelothngai ning leaph sakkar( tukaphlieng) del a l laoh ban banhchouh pileu mekh haey daoysaar vea trong ban thveu aoy dei meanchivit laengvinh banteabpi kar slab ( kmean chicheate) robsa vea promteang karophlasabdaur tisa robsa khyal noh chea phosdo tang samreab krom del svengoyl
